Moose::Autobox::List(3pm) User Contributed Perl Documentation Moose::Autobox::List(3pm)

NAME

Moose::Autobox::List - the List role

VERSION

version 0.16

DESCRIPTION

This is a role to describes a List interface. This is not meant to be any specific Perl type, but instead an interface that certain Perl types might implement. Currently only Moose::Autobox::Array implements this.

METHODS

"reduce"
"zip"
"meta"

REQUIRED METHODS

"head"
"tail"
"join"
"length"
"map"
"grep"
"reverse"
"sort"
